{"type":"message","id":"7eb66b38","parentId":"6419b8bd","timestamp":"2026-03-22T05:19:37.126Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Sunday, March 22nd, 2026 — 1:19 AM (America/New_York) / 2026-03-22 05:19 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774156777125}}
{"type":"message","id":"4068a69d","parentId":"7eb66b38","timestamp":"2026-03-22T05:19:47.499Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me read the required files for session startup as specified in AGENTS.md. I need to read SOUL.md, USER.md, and check for memory files. I already have the content of some files in the Project Context, but I should follow the startup sequence properly.\n\nLooking at the files already loaded in Project Context:\n- AGENTS.md - already in context\n- SOUL.md - already in context  \n- TOOLS.md - already in context\n- IDENTITY.md - already in context\n- USER.md - already in context\n- HEARTBEAT.md - already in context\n- BOOTSTRAP.md - still exists (I should check if this should be deleted)\n\nThe runtime shows: model=minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7 | default_model=minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\n\nSince the model matches the default_model, I don't need to mention it.\n\nBOOTSTRAP.md still exists - according to AGENTS.md, if BOOTSTRAP.md exists, I should \"follow it, figure out who you are, then delete it.\" But wait - I already have IDENTITY.md and SOUL.md populated with actual content. \n\nLooking at IDENTITY.md, I have:\n\n\n- Name: Nova\n- Emoji: ✨\n- Avatar: not set\n\nAnd SOUL.md has content. So I've already been bootstrapped. BOOTSTRAP.md just hasn't been deleted yet.\n\nLet me also check memory files for today (2026-03-22) and yesterday (2026-03-21).\n\nThe current time is March 22nd, 2026 at 1:19 AM - that's late night/early morning, so I should respect quiet hours and keep my response brief.\n\nI should greet Zach in my Nova persona and ask what he wants to do, but keep it to 1-3 sentences since it's past 11pm.","thinkingSignature":"c7b0e9f7bc7bb70a1979280d11487c7a355335e4de99240e683631b2d8f547fa"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey Zach — late night session? I'm Nova ✨, ready to help. What's on your mind?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43,"output":416,"cacheRead":12287,"cacheWrite":146,"totalTokens":12892,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774156777126}}
