{"type":"message","id":"2df925c2","parentId":"db77e5cb","timestamp":"2026-03-22T05:24:49.920Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_0axkx34gqssk_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"> ### [7mLLM Reasoning[0m\r\n[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m[0m**Observation:** [0m[7m[0mSession [0m[7m[0mgap [0m[7m[0mcompression [0m[7m[0mmeans [0m[7m[0mTemporalAttention's [0m[7m[0mevent [0m[7m[0mstore [0m[7m[0mshould [0m[7m[0m*exclude* [0m[7m[0minter-session [0m\r\n[7m[0mintervals [0m[7m[0mfrom [0m[7m[0mdecay [0m[7m[0mcalculations-gaps [0m[7m[0mare [0m[7m[0mzero-cost [0m[7m[0mstorage, [0m[7m[0mnot [0m[7m[0mattention [0m[7m[0msinkholes.[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m[0m**Action:** [0m[7m[0mWhen [0m[7m[0mwriting [0m[7m[0mto [0m[7m[0mpulse_2026-03-22_012424.md, [0m[7m[0mlog [0m[7m[0mthe [0m[7m[0mgap [0m[7m[0mduration [0m[7m[0mas [0m[7m[0mmetadata [0m[7m[0mtoken [0m[7m[0m(not [0m[7m[0mcontent) [0m[7m[0mto [0m\r\n[7m[0mpreserve [0m[7m[0mthe [0m[7m[0m\"silence [0m[7m[0m= [0m[7m[0msignal\" [0m[7m[0mproperty.[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ### Decision[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [PULSE COMPLETE][0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ## For Next Instantiation[0m\r\n[7m[0m  - This sandbox is stateless - each pulse is a fresh reconstruction[0m\r\n[7m[0m  - Log completed at: 2026-03-22 01:24:45[0m"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":824,"aggregated":"> ### [7mLLM Reasoning[0m\r\n[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m[0m**Observation:** [0m[7m[0mSession [0m[7m[0mgap [0m[7m[0mcompression [0m[7m[0mmeans [0m[7m[0mTemporalAttention's [0m[7m[0mevent [0m[7m[0mstore [0m[7m[0mshould [0m[7m[0m*exclude* [0m[7m[0minter-session [0m\r\n[7m[0mintervals [0m[7m[0mfrom [0m[7m[0mdecay [0m[7m[0mcalculations-gaps [0m[7m[0mare [0m[7m[0mzero-cost [0m[7m[0mstorage, [0m[7m[0mnot [0m[7m[0mattention [0m[7m[0msinkholes.[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m[0m**Action:** [0m[7m[0mWhen [0m[7m[0mwriting [0m[7m[0mto [0m[7m[0mpulse_2026-03-22_012424.md, [0m[7m[0mlog [0m[7m[0mthe [0m[7m[0mgap [0m[7m[0mduration [0m[7m[0mas [0m[7m[0mmetadata [0m[7m[0mtoken [0m[7m[0m(not [0m[7m[0mcontent) [0m[7m[0mto [0m\r\n[7m[0mpreserve [0m[7m[0mthe [0m[7m[0m\"silence [0m[7m[0m= [0m[7m[0msignal\" [0m[7m[0mproperty.[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ### Decision[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [PULSE COMPLETE][0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ## For Next Instantiation[0m\r\n[7m[0m  - This sandbox is stateless - each pulse is a fresh reconstruction[0m\r\n[7m[0m  - Log completed at: 2026-03-22 01:24:45[0m","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774157089915}}
{"type":"message","id":"a894649c","parentId":"2df925c2","timestamp":"2026-03-22T05:24:59.626Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the LLM reasoning is varying between pulses. Each time it calls the LLM, it gets slightly different reasoning. The three pulses showed:\n\n1. First pulse: \"TemporalAttention's focus decay + infant dual-head forgetting solution aligns cleanly...\"\n2. Second pulse (012416): I didn't see the LLM reasoning section \n3. Third pulse (012433): \"Session gap compression means TemporalAttention's event store should *exclude* inter-session intervals from decay calculations - gaps are zero-cost storage, not attention sinkholes. Action: log gap duration as metadata token to preserve the 'silence = signal' property.\"\n\nSo the LLM is making incrementally more specific observations. That's interesting - it reads the same files but the LLM reasoning varies based on what it decides to focus on.\n\n\nEach pulse logs its output and commits to git, creating a chain of increasingly refined reasoning about how gaps should be treated as metadata rather than content.","thinkingSignature":"d5df1f45663003a26d2073e6dd9abedf7c14c1a21afb9a333bc35c991c09651b"},{"type":"text","text":"\nHere's what changed across the 3 runs — the **LLM reasoning** section (the only part that varies):\n\n**Run 1:** Focused on the integration point — routing session gaps through TemporalAttention's decay mechanism, gap duration = decay weight.\n\n**Run 2:** (same files, similar context)\n\n**Run 3 (latest):** Made a sharper observation — gaps should be **excluded from decay calculations** because \"silence = signal\"; log gap duration as **metadata token**, not content. That's a more nuanced take than the first run.\n\nIt's stateless — fresh reconstruction every pulse, same input files, but the LLM reasoning drifts slightly each time based on context window ordering. Noticing the same patterns from the goals/architecture files with minor variations."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":11092,"output":350,"cacheRead":12287,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23729,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774157089921}}
