{"type":"message","id":"9060c564","parentId":"0f522749","timestamp":"2026-03-22T05:32:14.864Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_4gv7i8eqmp4k_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"> ## [7mLLM Response[0m\r\n[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m[0mLooking [0m[7m[0mat [0m[7m[0mthe [0m[7m[0mpending [0m[7m[0mactions, [0m[7m[0mI [0m[7m[0mneed [0m[7m[0mto [0m[7m[0mdefine [0m[7m[0m`significance` [0m[7m[0mscoring [0m[7m[0mfor [0m[7m[0mpulse [0m[7m[0mcontent. [0m[7m[0mThis [0m[7m[0mis [0m[7m[0mfoundational [0m[7m[0mfor [0m\r\n[7m[0m? [0m[7m[0mtuning [0m[7m[0mand [0m[7m[0mcompression [0m[7m[0mmeasurement. [0m[7m[0mI'll [0m[7m[0mcreate [0m[7m[0ma [0m[7m[0mconcrete [0m[7m[0mspecification [0m[7m[0mfor [0m[7m[0mhow [0m[7m[0mto [0m[7m[0mscore [0m[7m[0mpulse [0m[7m[0msignificance.[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ### OBSERVATION[0m\r\n[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m[0mThe [0m[7m[0mgap-decay [0m[7m[0msynthesis [0m[7m[0mis [0m[7m[0mcomplete, [0m[7m[0mbut [0m[7m[0mwe [0m[7m[0mlack [0m[7m[0ma [0m[7m[0mconcrete [0m[7m[0mdefinition [0m[7m[0mof [0m[7m[0mwhat [0m[7m[0mmakes [0m[7m[0mpulse [0m[7m[0mcontent [0m[7m[0m\"significant\" [0m[7m[0m- [0m\r\n[7m[0mthe [0m[7m[0mcore [0m[7m[0mmetric [0m[7m[0mneeded [0m[7m[0mto [0m[7m[0mtune [0m[7m[0m? [0m[7m[0mand [0m[7m[0mmeasure [0m[7m[0mcompression [0m[7m[0meffectiveness.[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ### ACTION[0m\r\n[7m[0m  Create a significance scoring specification that defines how to evaluate pulse content for decay decisions.[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ### MUTATION[0m\r\n[7m[0m  ```[0m\r\n[7m[0m  old_text: (new file)[0m\r\n[7m[0m  new_text: # Significance Scoring for Pulse Content[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ## Purpose[0m\r\n[7m[0m  Defines how to score pulse content significance for Breakaway's gap-decay mechanism.[0m\r\n[7m[0m  This metric determines which content survives across session boundaries.[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ## Scoring Dimensions[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ### 1. Novelty Score (N)[0m\r\n[7m[0m  Measures how new/innovative the content is compared to prior pulses.[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ```[0m\r\n[7m[0m  N = 1 - (overlapping_concepts / total_concepts)[0m\r\n[7m[0m  ```[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  - Range: [0.0, 1.0][0m\r\n[7m[0m  - 0.0 = fully redundant with prior content[0m\r\n[7m[0m  - 1.0 = completely novel content[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ### 2. Utility Score (U)[0m\r\n[7m[0m  Measures task completion progress and goal advancement.[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ```[0m\r\n[7m[0m  U = �goals_advanced / �time_elapsed[0m\r\n[7m[0m  ```[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  - Range: [0.0, 1.0][0m\r\n[7m[0m  - 0.0 = no progress despite time spent[0m\r\n[7m[0m  - 1.0 = maximum goal advancement[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ### 3. Complexity Score (C)[0m\r\n[7m[0m  Measures information density and structural complexity.[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ```[0m\r\n[7m[0m  C = unique_entities / total_tokens[0m\r\n[7m[0m  ```[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  - Range: [0.0, 1.0][0m\r\n[7m[0m  - Higher = more distinct concepts per word[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ## Combined Significance Score[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ```[0m\r\n[7m[0m  significance = �*N + �*U + ?*C[0m\r\n[7m[0m  ```[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  Where � + � + ? = 1.0[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ### Default Weights[0m\r\n[7m[0m  ```[0m\r\n[7m[0m  � = 0.4  # Novelty weighted highest (Breakaway's unique contribution)[0m\r\n[7m[0m  � = 0.4  # Utility matters equally[0m\r\n[7m[0m  ? = 0.2  # Complexity is supporting metric[0m\r\n[7m[0m  ```[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ## Threshold for Survival[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  - **survive_threshold = 0.5** (configurable)[0m\r\n[7m[0m  - Pulses scoring above threshold  preserve full content[0m\r\n[7m[0m  - Pulses scoring below threshold  compress to summary[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ## Integration with ?[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  The significance score directly informs ? decisions:[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ```[0m\r\n[7m[0m  if significance < survive_threshold:[0m\r\n[7m[0m      apply_decay(?=0.7)    # Aggressive compression[0m\r\n[7m[0m  else:[0m"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":547,"aggregated":"> ## [7mLLM Response[0m\r\n[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m[0mLooking [0m[7m[0mat [0m[7m[0mthe [0m[7m[0mpending [0m[7m[0mactions, [0m[7m[0mI [0m[7m[0mneed [0m[7m[0mto [0m[7m[0mdefine [0m[7m[0m`significance` [0m[7m[0mscoring [0m[7m[0mfor [0m[7m[0mpulse [0m[7m[0mcontent. [0m[7m[0mThis [0m[7m[0mis [0m[7m[0mfoundational [0m[7m[0mfor [0m\r\n[7m[0m? [0m[7m[0mtuning [0m[7m[0mand [0m[7m[0mcompression [0m[7m[0mmeasurement. [0m[7m[0mI'll [0m[7m[0mcreate [0m[7m[0ma [0m[7m[0mconcrete [0m[7m[0mspecification [0m[7m[0mfor [0m[7m[0mhow [0m[7m[0mto [0m[7m[0mscore [0m[7m[0mpulse [0m[7m[0msignificance.[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ### OBSERVATION[0m\r\n[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m[0mThe [0m[7m[0mgap-decay [0m[7m[0msynthesis [0m[7m[0mis [0m[7m[0mcomplete, [0m[7m[0mbut [0m[7m[0mwe [0m[7m[0mlack [0m[7m[0ma [0m[7m[0mconcrete [0m[7m[0mdefinition [0m[7m[0mof [0m[7m[0mwhat [0m[7m[0mmakes [0m[7m[0mpulse [0m[7m[0mcontent [0m[7m[0m\"significant\" [0m[7m[0m- [0m\r\n[7m[0mthe [0m[7m[0mcore [0m[7m[0mmetric [0m[7m[0mneeded [0m[7m[0mto [0m[7m[0mtune [0m[7m[0m? [0m[7m[0mand [0m[7m[0mmeasure [0m[7m[0mcompression [0m[7m[0meffectiveness.[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ### ACTION[0m\r\n[7m[0m  Create a significance scoring specification that defines how to evaluate pulse content for decay decisions.[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ### MUTATION[0m\r\n[7m[0m  ```[0m\r\n[7m[0m  old_text: (new file)[0m\r\n[7m[0m  new_text: # Significance Scoring for Pulse Content[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ## Purpose[0m\r\n[7m[0m  Defines how to score pulse content significance for Breakaway's gap-decay mechanism.[0m\r\n[7m[0m  This metric determines which content survives across session boundaries.[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ## Scoring Dimensions[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ### 1. Novelty Score (N)[0m\r\n[7m[0m  Measures how new/innovative the content is compared to prior pulses.[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0