ward defined goals |[0m\r\n[7m[0m  | `error_recovery` | 0.10 | Documents or resolves errors |[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ### Calculation[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ```[0m\r\n[7m[0m  def compute_significance(pulse_text, previous_summaries):[0m\r\n[7m[0m      novelty = 1.0 - (overlap_with_recent(pulse_text, previous_summaries) / max_overlap)[0m\r\n[7m[0m      [0m\r\n[7m[0m      decision = 1.0 if contains_keywords(pulse_text, [\"DECISION\", \"CHOOSE\", \"COMMIT\", \"SELECT\"]) else 0.0[0m\r\n[7m[0m      [0m\r\n[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m[0msynthesis [0m[7m[0m= [0m[7m[0m1.0 [0m[7m[0mif [0m[7m[0mcontains_keywords(pulse_text, [0m[7m[0m[\"SYNTHESIS\", [0m[7m[0m\"INSIGHT\", [0m[7m[0m\"THUS\", [0m[7m[0m\"THEREFORE\", [0m[7m[0m\"CONCLUDES\"]) [0m\r\n[7m[0melse [0m[7m[0m0.0[0m\r\n[7m[0m      [0m\r\n[7m[0m      task_progress = measure_progress_markers(pulse_text)[0m\r\n[7m[0m      [0m\r\n[7m[0m      error_recovery = 1.0 if contains_keywords(pulse_text, [\"ERROR\", \"FIX\", \"RESOLVE\", \"BUG\"]) else 0.0[0m\r\n[7m[0m      [0m\r\n[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m[0mscore [0m[7m[0m= [0m[7m[0m(0.30 [0m[7m[0m* [0m[7m[0mnovelty) [0m[7m[0m+ [0m[7m[0m(0.25 [0m[7m[0m* [0m[7m[0mdecision) [0m[7m[0m+ [0m[7m[0m(0.20 [0m[7m[0m* [0m[7m[0msynthesis) [0m[7m[0m+ [0m[7m[0m(0.15 [0m[7m[0m* [0m[7m[0mtask_progress) [0m[7m[0m+ [0m[7m[0m(0.10 [0m[7m[0m* [0m\r\n[7m[0merror_recovery)[0m\r\n[7m[0m      [0m\r\n[7m[0m      return round(score, 3)[0m\r\n[7m[0m  ```[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  ### Threshold for Preservation[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n[7m[0m  - `score >= 0.5`  Full preservation (enter long-term memory)[0m\r\n[7m[0m  - `0.3 <= score < 0.5`  Partial preservation (compressed summary)[0m\r\n[7m[0m  - `score < 0.3`  Minimal preservation (reference only)[0m\r\n[7m[0m  [0m\r\n> - Proposed [7mmutation[0ms waiting: 0[0m\r\n[7m[0m  - Completed at: 2026-03-22 02:21:55[0m"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":544,"aggregated":"> ## Applied [7mMutation[0